content:
These are the available InsProviderNetworkService methods.

IMPORTANT
These services are retired from the Insurance Winter '22 release onward.

InsProviderNetworkService:cloneNetwork
Use this service in an OmniScript to clone a Provider Network.
InsProviderNetworkService:getProviders
Use this service to get a list of Providers and Provider Networks, based on the contact name, postal code, or profile attributes.
InsProviderNetworkService:getProvidersByArea
Use this service to get all providers and their networks for a given geographical location.
InsProviderNetworkService:getProvidersByNameOrNPI
Use this service to allow users to search for Providers using a search key.
InsProviderNetworkService:getProvidersDetail
This service allows you to retrieve Provider information, including group affiliations and locations.
title: Retired Insurance Provider Network Service Methods
